claim: Flublok is approved for adults 18 years and older
explanation: The image shows safety/reactogenicity data from clinical trials of Flublok in adults age 50 and older (e.g. “a total of 2050 adults age 50 and older received Flublok…” and tables of local and systemic reactions in an older‐adult cohort). There is no mention of subjects aged 18–49 or an approval age range beginning at 18 years. Therefore, this excerpt does not provide evidence that Flublok is approved for adults 18 years and older.
